{"tid":1645033,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"홍콩중문대학교 공개 청문히","createTime":"2019-10-10T17:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T18:19:25.000Z","uid":319630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ed5819e302a5f4e0aa0fd67250579fca668672","tid":1645033,"uid":319630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:59:48.000Z","msg":"홍콩중문대학교 공개 청문히에서 이 여학생은 Kwai Chung경찰서에서 손을 잠그고 &quot;가슴을 쓰다듬었다&quot;는 남자 경찰관에게 체포되었다고 발언했다. 이후 산욱링홀딩센터(구치소)에 문이 없는 방에서 수색을 당했다.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n홍콩 중문 대학교 충장님께 : ...경찰측에게 때림을 맞고 성폭행을 당하고 나서 저희 (시위 때문에 체포 된 자들)에게 첫 말씀은 유리창문 한장을 깼으니 비판한것을 보다 먼저 관심을 기울이주셨으면 좋겠습니다.... ㅠㅠ<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WH4Km2U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWH4Km2U.png&h=563596bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32d89775cd6cff12922adfafc0bc822d02823f0a","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"14b788dff24320d098450affdcf1cb27bd14b502","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8462d8e530b03de13fb5f0ce2564a8e08f61392d","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"a75c48ba6510cfb32cad437f8cb19cc3becce3f5","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:35.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ec7a4f4f04159c1cd5d6d632d341cda3230fed31","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"947a7941cc9903e4d5c7eadf20fdc393a63be989","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:58.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"66c6da21c95162933e75cbc54038b20be361481f","tid":1645033,"uid":218391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:18:09.000Z","